The compatible combination of TM algorithms with TC algorithms is very significant to have the extended lifespan of WSNs. A better performance of WSNs employed in a nuclear power plant using different combinations of TC and TM algorithms is represented in this work. Our proposed approach is simulated on 1014Ã1014m2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
